	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Intentional PPU hum...</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think the video would overpower the audio if you connected them. For one, it has 68-ohm impedance, while audio has 150 ohms. And the video signal is mostly a full-modulation pulse wave at low frequency, very loud.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


