		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />&quot;Music that has something to do with what you see&quot; has a long standing history in game use, but the specific bit about <em>using the PPU</em> implies using the one thing the PPU can do well: be a 4 bit DAC at 5MHz.<br /><br />Playing (optionally transformed) level data as sound is about as relevant to the PPU as it is to a beverage one might drink while playing.

		

